Regulators: board-n1-pmic.c

Battery:
	Maxim MAX17050
	kwds: max17050

Screen:
	Wacom I2C touchscreen
	kwds: i2c wacom
	board file: arch/arm/mach-exynos/board-n1-input.c

Audio Codec:
	SoC I2S Wolfson WM5102 Adonis Univ Arizona
	kwds: i2s codec adonis_univ wm5102 arizona

	Example:

	codec: wm5102@1a {
		compatible = "wlf,wm5102";
		reg = <0x1a>;
		interrupts = <347>;
		interrupt-controller;
		#interrupt-cells = <2>;
        	interrupt-parent = <&gic>;

		gpio-controller;
		#gpio-cells = <2>;

		wlf,gpio-defaults = <
			0x00000000 /* AIF1TXLRCLK */
			0xffffffff
			0xffffffff
			0xffffffff
			0xffffffff
		>;
	};